reviewText: very funny movie  great watch Jill at one of her best

I love this movie!  I am waiting for it to become availabe in DVD.  Jill Eikenberry and Michael Tucker have done it again!  I just love those two, and guess what!  They are married to each other in real life!
I had been looking for this movie for what seemed like forever and I was sooooooooo happy when I finally found it and at an excellent price! Thank you!!

This movie with real life marrieds keeps me entertained every time I watch it.  The "attack" scene in the living room where the husband jumps on the coffee table is hysterical to me every time!  This couple is great together and they should make more movies as a team.  Well worth adding to your comedy collection.

I  have  searched  high  and  low  to  buy  this  movie  and  wish  it  was  cheaper  so  I  could.  I  love  it though.  It  will  keep  you  suspecting  and  laughing  forever.  As  soon  as  the  price  drops,  it's  mine!
